                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">HoTT - best one to get period
<br />
Health Enhancement - extra hp helps everyone
<br />
Mana Enhancement - extra mana good for clerics
<br />
Offensive Enhancement -  melee love an extra 50atk
<br />
Delegate Main Assist - good for grouping for less mez breaks
<br />
Spell Awareness - good to see when the mob is casting CH to interrupt
<br />
Find Path to PC - for that group member who gets lost 
<br />
NPC Health - ehhh...works sometimes so you can see mob health when not targeting
<br />

<br />
Those are what I have and the order I got them...everything else just seems like a waste of time...</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
